    "---\n",
    "## Dataset 1 — World GDP Growth rate %\n",
    "\n",
    "| | |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| **Source** | Kaggle GDP growth rate data — Indicator \"Annual GDP growth rate (year-over-year % change in real GDP)\" |\n",
    "| **Coverage** | 196 entries (countries + regional aggregates) × 44 years (1980–2024) |\n",
    "| **Format** | **Wide** — one row per country, one column per year |\n",
    "| **What one row means** | A single country's GDP Growth rate % value for every year from 1980 to 2024 |\n",
    "\n",
    "This dataset tracks annual GDP growth rates for 196 countries from 1980 to 2024 — 45 years of economic history in a single wide-format table. This dataset also contains some regional aggregates that needs to be fixed"
   ]
